@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to SignWiz!</h1>
    <p>Learn to Sign, Play to Learn</p>
</div>

<div class="container about-container">
    <div class="about-heading">
        <h2>About SignWiz</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-content">
        <p>Welcome to SignWiz, your ultimate companion for learning sign language through interactive games and quizzes. Our mission is to make sign language accessible and fun for everyone, whether you are a beginner or looking to improve your skills.</p>
        <p>At SignWiz, we believe in the power of interactive learning. Our app combines educational content with engaging games to provide a unique and effective learning experience. With a variety of quizzes, games, and resources, SignWiz helps you master sign language at your own pace.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container get-started-container mt-5">
    <div class="get-started-heading text-center">
        <h2>Get Started with SignWiz</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="get-started-content text-center mt-4">
        <p>Ready to start your sign language learning journey? Here’s how to get started:</p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3>Start on the Learning Page</h3>
                <p>Head over to our <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Learn">Learning Page</a> where you’ll find structured lessons and resources to help you grasp the basics and beyond.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3>Play Interactive Games</h3>
                <p>Jump right into the fun with our <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Games">Interactive Games</a>. These games are designed to make learning sign language enjoyable and effective through active engagement.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container about-container mt-5">
    <div class="about-heading">
        <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-content">
        <p>Connect with other learners, share your progress, and get support from our community. Follow us on social media and join our forums to stay updated on the latest features and events.</p>
        <p><a href="https://linktr.ee/signwiz">Join the Community</a></p>
    </div>
</div>